name: Paul Weller at Eden Print
description:
This was shot at Eden Projects Sessions 2009.  I have always been a bit of a fan of Paul Weller, and was pleased to be given a press pass to go shoot the gig.

Hand printed, exclusive edition 1 of 5 prints, numbered and signed on the back. This was printed by me in my dark room on 17th Jul 2009.  5 were printed on to Ilford Pearl Multigrade IV RC Delux paper.  Size is 8 x 10 inch (20.3 x 25.4cm)

name: Bridges of the Mind
description:
This was shot near Tower Bridge in London.  The buildings used to be warehouses and the bridges between the building allowed for movement of goods.  Nowadays they are private residences and the bridges are used as balconies. These prints display some slight printing errors, and hence are slightly cheaper. 
  
Hand printed, exclusive edition 1 of 3 prints, numbered and signed on the back. This was printed by me in my dark room on to Ilford Pearl Multigrade IV RC Delux paper.  Size is 8 x 10 inch (20.3 x 25.4cm)

name: Southsea Pier Ride
description:
I spent alot of time in Southsea over the years, and on this recent trip to visit my buddie Gonella, we went on a photo mission on our bikes. The shot is of a sketch funfair ride on this little pier.  This was shot with an old Russian panoramic film camera.
 
Hand printed, exclusive edition 1 of 5 prints, numbered and signed on the back. This was printed by me in my dark room on to Ilford Pearl Multigrade IV RC Delux paper.  Size is 8 x 10 inch (20.3 x 25.4cm)
